      </section>

      <h2>More Information</h2>
      <p>
        Ruby Skillz is a comprehensive online tutoring platform for middle
        school students. We offer personalized one-on-one tutoring in a variety
        of subjects, including math, science, English, and social studies.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our tutors are experienced educators who are passionate about helping
        students succeed. We use a personalized approach to tutoring, tailoring
        our sessions to each student's individual needs and learning style.
        Whether your child is struggling in a particular subject or simply wants
        to improve their grades, Ruby Skillz can help.
      </p>
